					text = <"mica_holding">
					description = <"The Gupta Perioperative Risk Calculator estimates the 30-day risk of myocardial infarction or cardiac arrest following surgery, based on NSQIP data. Developed using logistic regression, it includes only five clinical variables and is widely used to guide perioperative risk discussions. While derived from historical surgical cohorts, it remains validated and relevant in contemporary practice for non-cardiac surgeries.">
